      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several visible scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows signs of regular use, including some wear on the driver's seat upholstery and carpet. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
