    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. You\u2019ll love how smooth it feels on the road! It\u2019s clean, well-loved, and ready for its next big adventure. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the iconic S54-powered chassis. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power delivery to a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. Crucially, the subframe has been reinforced to handle lateral torsional loads, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly health. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings, offering the precise turn-in and feedback characteristic of the MacPherson strut and multi-link rear setup. While the finish shows light patina, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for high-performance driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Solid runner. Routine maintenance performed. Minor surface scratches. Interior clean. Title ready for transfer.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the ideal balance between a pristine collector's piece and a dependable daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, honest signs of use consistent with a well-cared-for life on the road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free, with supple upholstery and a dashboard where every electronic component, climate control setting, and gauge functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has been maintained with a rigorous, no-expense-spared approach to preventative service. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the handling remains tight and responsive. For the buyer who demands mechanical transparency and a polished presentation, this car offers a complete and worry-free package.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
